Package project.model

Class Appointment

java.lang.Object
project.model.Appointment
public class Appointment extends Object
Represents an appointment in the application. It includes information such as the appointment's ID, customer ID, user ID, contact ID, title, description, location, type, and start and end times.
Author:
Teksong Eap
